latestIgtvVideos.title: Subtweet For What? #KocktailsWithKarly
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Welcome the FUCK back! #KocktailsWithKarly
.
In today’s episode we’re talking about the (not so) elusive SUBTWEET…
.
Karly hares her recent subtweet drama, why she thinks we’re all too grown to be subtweeting each other and more. She also tells it like it is and lays down that if your hater aren’t paying your bills or your genuine friend…. their opinions don’t ever matter
.
She also rehashes the MLM drama from last week and says her peace on that
.
Don’t forget, you can check out Karly’s brand Confidence Club here: @shopconfidenceclub
.
*RECIPE DEETS*
.
2oz silver tequila (@patron)
1oz honey syrup
1/2 oz lemon juice
4oz champagne or sparkling wine (@lamarcaprocessco, @lamarcaprocessco_ca)
*optional* egg whites, thyme garnish
.
combine tequila, honey syrup, and lemon juice in cocktail shaker with ice. Shake to combine. Pour into glass and top with champagne or sparkling wine
.
Enjoy!

Are y'all ready to dive back into Kocktails with Karly? Let me know how you enjoyed the episode below!

*RECIPE DEETS*
.
1oz vodka (I use @prairieorganic)
1oz coffee liqueur (@kahlua)
1oz Irish cream (@baileysofficial …. but I used 2oz)
1/2 cup milk or heavy cream
1 cup ice
*OPTIONAL* chocolate sauce to taste, whipped cream, mint to garnish
.
Mix vodka, liqueur, Irish cream, milk, and ice in blender. Blend until smooth. *optional* stir in chocolate sauce, garnish with whipped cream and mint.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Welcome the FUCK back! #KocktailsWithKarly
.

.
In today's episode, I'm dishing all about the fact there are NO new ideas! We chat persona experiences, @shitbloggerspost , how to react when someone copies you, and MUCH MORE
.
Are y'all ready to dive back into Kocktails with Karly? Let me know how you enjoyed the episode below!
.
*RECIPE DEETS*
.
3oz grapefruit juice
1oz pink peppercorn simple syrup
2oz silver tequila (I used @patron)
*Optional dash of soda water
.
Mix juice, syrup, and tequila, in a cocktail shaker, filled half full with ice. Strain into glass. Add ice and optional soda water. Enjoy!

latestIgtvVideos.title: “Uneducated” is Not an Excuse
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In the past week I have had many conversations with fellow influencers and people with platforms in the DMs. The number 1 excuse I have been hearing as to why they have been silent is that they are "uneducated".
.
Now, more than ever, we live in an age of information where the resources, guides, people that are speaking on these topics are easy and accessible to find.
.
Stop using being "uneducated" as an excuse to be passive. We see what you're doing.
.
#blm #georgefloyd #blacklivesmatter #speakup #blackvoicesheard

IT’S FINALLY DONE 👏🏽

can y’all believe this kitchen project has taken me SIX MONTHS??

since then I’ve gone from peel and stick tile to faux rock sheets to tearing out the old backsplash… just to get to this beadboard backsplash of my dreams!

this project was 100% a lesson in “figuring it out” and having faith in myself and my abilities because it was CONSTANTLY dancing on my nerves

who knew making over a kitchen would be harder than building a library from scratch???

ANYWAYS!

we’re SO CLOSE to the finish line in here… all that’s left is painting these cabinets, installing new hardware, and *maybe* upgrading the countertops?? who knows!!

so make sure to follow along for our grand reveal coming soon 🔨

#kitchenmakeover #diyrenovation #diyhome #homemakeover #diykitchenmakeover

WEAR THE SHORTS 🗣️ inspo: @itsyourdest 🫶🏼

and the bikini, and the skirt, and the dress, and WHATEVER you want!!!

life is too damn short to be worrying about what other people ✨might✨ be thinking about your body…. because truth is?? 

everyone is too wrapped up in their own lives to even really notice!

so rock the fuck out of those denim shorts, stun in that backless dress, and wear whatever tf you want this summer because your body is BEAUTIFUL 💕

#bodyposi #weartheshorts #bikinibody #summerbody #bodyacceptance #everybodyisabikinibody

NO MORE BACKSPLASH 🗣️🗣️🗣️

finally back at you with part 4 of my kitchen makeover where I finally bite the bullet and rip off the backsplash!

from peel and stick to faux panels, I really tried EVERYTHING to avoid taking off this backsplash but who would have thought a loose electrical wire would lead me to ripping it ALL off

I’m SO excited to make my original vision come to life in here now that we’ve got a clean slate to work with and I can’t wait to get this kitchen rolling along
